description: Nathan Topps is cool guy to work with. He is always committed to give a good performance and it shows in this behind-the-scene look at one of his scene. Lots of never-seen-before shots showing him having fun in between takes. This one is filled with bloopers in over 30 minutes of raw footage. A must see for all hairy chests lovers and for Nathan's fans!
series: MSKBNS_0024 - Behind the Scene with Nathan Topps
title: Behind the Scene with Nathan Topps
